  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK234">
<l>nilavarai nīḷpuka ḻāṟṟiṟ pulavaraip</l>
<l>pōṟṟātu puttē ḷulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one has acquired extensive fame within the limits of this earth, the world of the Gods will no longer praise those sages who have attained that world.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
